@page
@model ContosoCrafts.WebSite.Pages.PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<!-- Main container with vertical margin -->
<div class="container mt-5 text-white">

    <!-- Page title -->
    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-center" style="font-family: 'Bangers', cursive; text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px black;">
        PRIVACY POLICY
    </h1>

    <!-- Last updated date in styled box -->
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center mb-4">
        <div style="background-color: rgba(255, 193, 7, 0.95); color: black; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.1rem; box-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">
            Last updated: <span style="color: #b30000;">May 9, 2025</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main policy content container -->
    <div class="bg-dark bg-opacity-75 rounded-4 shadow-lg p-5 mx-auto" style="max-width: 900px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8;">

        <!-- Intro paragraph -->
        <p>
            At <strong>Avengers Encyclopedia</strong>, we respect your privacy and are committed to protecting any personal information you share with us.
            This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information we collect, how we use it, and the choices you have.
        </p>

        <!-- Section 1: Information Collection -->
        <h5 class="text-warning mt-4 fw-bold" style="font-family: 'Bangers', cursive;">1. INFORMATION WE COLLECT</h5>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Personal Data:</strong> If you contact us or submit a form, we may collect your name, email address, and any other information you provide.</li>
            <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> We may collect information such as your browser type, operating system, IP address, and pages visited on our site to improve user experience.</li>
            <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Our site uses cookies to enhance functionality and gather analytics.</li>
        </ul>

        <!-- Section 2: How Information Is Used -->
        <h5 class="text-warning mt-4 fw-bold" style="font-family: 'Bangers', cursive;">2. HOW WE USE YOUR INFORMATION</h5>
        <ul>
            <li>To personalize your experience and display content tailored to your interests.</li>
            <li>To improve our website based on user behavior and feedback.</li>
            <li>To respond to inquiries and support requests.</li>
        </ul>

        <!-- Section 3: Third-Party Services -->
        <h5 class="text-warning mt-4 fw-bold" style="font-family: 'Bangers', cursive;">3. THIRD-PARTY SERVICES</h5>
        <p>We may use third-party tools such as Google Analytics to better understand how users interact with our site. These services may collect data as per their own privacy policies.</p>

        <!-- Section 4: Data Security -->
        <h5 class="text-warning mt-4 fw-bold" style="font-family: 'Bangers', cursive;">4. DATA SECURITY</h5>
        <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.</p>

        <!-- Section 5: User Rights -->
        <h5 class="text-warning mt-4 fw-bold" style="font-family: 'Bangers', cursive;">5. YOUR RIGHTS</h5>
        <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete any personal data we have about you. You can contact us at any time to request changes or ask questions.</p>

        <!-- Section 6: Children's Privacy -->
        <h5 class="text-warning mt-4 fw-bold" style="font-family: 'Bangers', cursive;">6. CHILDREN’S PRIVACY</h5>
        <p>Our website is not directed toward children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from minors without parental consent.</p>

        <!-- Section 7: Policy Updates -->
        <h5 class="text-warning mt-4 fw-bold" style="font-family: 'Bangers', cursive;">7. CHANGES TO THIS POLICY</h5>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

        <!-- Section 8: Contact Info -->
        <h5 class="text-warning mt-4 fw-bold" style="font-family: 'Bangers', cursive;">8. CONTACT US</h5>
        <p>
            If you have any questions about this policy or your personal data, please email us at:
            <a href="mailto:admin@avengersencyclopedia.com" class="text-info">admin@avengersencyclopedia.com</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
